，仅有1个尾喷口。而歼-35A是双发动机战机，有2个尾喷口。 这家美国权威军事媒体还不无揶揄地写道：“考虑到该办公室的责任是确保美军的F-35战机时刻待命，我们原以为他们的工作人员会非常熟悉这款战机的细节，可目前看来，事实并非如此。” 一些比较“毒舌”的美国网民也没有放过这个机会，其中一个美国网民指出：这个海报的右下角就有一个F-35标志，难道工作人员没想着对比一下吗？（环球时报新媒体）"},"attached_info":"CkEI1qqOpcO2v/N6EAMaCTExMTc4OTUzOCDs8NG5BjAAONABQAFyCjQwNjQ2MTcyNzV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"271 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-123966fd8b1a024096c67cfa1e505b57_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"2_1731838703.389457","card_id":"Q_596279235","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":596279235,"title":"老北京话“沏壶高的”是什么意思？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/596279235","type":"question","created":1681795950,"answer_count":146,"follower_count":231,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[491,1089,7598,34938,182301],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I1qqOpcO2v/N6EAMaCDk0Nzg3NjcwIO7W+KEGMAA45wFAAnIJNTk2Mjc5MjM1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"217 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-7f44f725537988930126eff5a497b3ff_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"3_1731838703.389761","card_id":"Q_4373331825","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":4373331825,"title":"泰森回应不敌 27 岁网红拳手，「6 月份我差点死在医院，最后一舞后没有遗憾了」，他目前健康状况如何？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/4373331825","type":"question","created":1731803146,"answer_count":19,"follower_count":30,"